<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">وَقيل:</span> هُوَ خُرُوج الخاصرتين.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>ثَجِل ثَجَلا وَهُوَ أثجل.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">والمُثَجَّل:</span> كالأثجل،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>لَا هِجْرَعا رِخْوا وَلَا مُثَجَّلا<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">وجُلَّة ثجلاء:</span> عَظِيمَة،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>باتوا يُعَشُّون القُطَيعاء ضيفهم ... وَعِنْدهم البَرْنِيُّ فِي جُلَل ثُجْلِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">ومزادة ثَجْلاء:</span> عَظِيمَة،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>مَشْى الروايا بالمَزَاد الأثْجَلِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>وَقد رُوِيَ بالنُّون يُرَاد بِهِ الْوَاسِع.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">والأثجل:</span> الْقطعَة الضخمة من اللَّيْل،<span class="c5"> قَالَ العجاج:</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وأقطعُ الأثجل بعد الأثجل<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c5">[مقلوبه:</span> <span class="c2">(ث ل ج)</span>]<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c5">الثَّلْج:</span> الَّذِي يسْقط من السَّمَاء.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>وَقد أثْلَج يَوْمنَا.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c5">وأثْلِجُوا:</span> دخلُوا فِي الثَّلج.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c5">وثُلِجوا:</span> أَصَابَهُم الثَّلْج.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c5">وَأَرْض مثلوجة:</span> كَذَلِك.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span><span class="c5">وَمَاء مثلوج:</span> مُبَرَّد بالثَّلْج؛<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span><a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>لَو ذقتَ فاها بعد نوم المُدْلِج ...<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>